headline: Home Depot (HD): Assessing Current Valuation After Recent Stock Gains
summary: If you’ve had your eye on Home Depot (HD) lately, chances are the recent move in the stock price has you wondering what might be next. Shares have climbed roughly 7% in the past month, prompting investors to question whether the home improvement giant is entering a fresh growth phase or simply riding broader market optimism. With Home Depot quietly posting steady gains in both revenues and net income, there are real questions surfacing about whether the market is reassessing the company’s...
